net.antidot.api.common

Class Service

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.antidot.api.common.Service

  • public class Service
extends java.lang.Object
    Antidot search service.

    Search service provided by Antidot. Antidot search service is identified by a number and a status. These values are provided by Antidot integration team.
